<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
BPacket

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
the UDP packet used to transport a single frame

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
A #BPacket consists of a mcu_frame_header struct followed by the
actual frame data. It corresponds to a single animation frame.
</para>

